{"tid":2174629,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"習近平對糧食浪費宣戰，推進「光盤行動」","createTime":"2020-08-26T04:01:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T05:00:06.000Z","uid":222970,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7ca9b63b182c593eafe69d6f57fbbaf84274db9d","tid":2174629,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T04:01:08.000Z","msg":"習近平對糧食浪費宣戰，推進「光盤行動」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reDEFVn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreDEFVn.jpg&h=8e946ecd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上個月在北京的一家餐館。官員希望餐館鼓勵食客少點菜，但並非所有人都願意承擔光盤行動的代價。 WU HONG/EPA, VIA SHUTTERSTOCK<br />\n<br />\n中國的監管者正在點名批評網上直播大吃大喝的人，指責他們助長過度消費。一所學校說，如果學生每天的剩飯超過了規定量的話，將禁止他們申請獎學金。一家餐館在門口放了一個讓顧客稱體重的電子秤，以免他們點太多的菜。<br />\n<br />\n中國最高領導人習近平向令人「觸目驚心、令人痛心」的糧食浪費宣戰，全國上下正在迅速做出響應，走極端者爭先恐後。<br />\n<br />\n雖然執政的中國共產黨一直尋求將習近平描繪為與官場的大吃大喝作鬥爭的人，但這場加強美食紀律的新運動針對的是公眾，而且帶有特殊的緊迫性。習近平說，中國公民應該在糧食安全問題上保持危機意識，因為新冠病毒大流行已暴露出了一些漏洞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20200824/china-food-waste-xi/zh-hant/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.nytimes.com%2Fchina%2F20200824%2Fchina-food-waste-xi%2Fzh-hant%2F&d=mfTbPTXtdXcWugdQC%2B6BDjY9GQwUZQLLS4G4eGYLUm4%3D&h=5321224b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20200824/china-food-waste-xi/zh-hant/</a>"},{"pid":"169dffa29d88add9b5d96f0c9e83c77b9ef4d19a","tid":2174629,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T04:01:48.000Z","msg":"阿平係唔係手足黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eac1faa71dcaa4e90edbb9ffa3b238f123c65e3","tid":2174629,"uid":55913,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T04:03:11.000Z","msg":"你自己咁撚肥叫人減食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgm